com.skratchdot.riff.wav

Interface ChunkSampler

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Chunk
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ChunkSamplerImpl

    public interface ChunkSampler
extends Chunk
    A representation of the model object 'Chunk Sampler'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Manufacturer
    • Product
    • Sample Period
    • Midi Unity Note
    • Midi Pitch Fraction
    • Smpte Format
    • Smpte Offset
    • Number Of Sample Loops
    • Sampler Data Size
    • Sample Loops
    • Sampler Data

    See Also:
    WavPackage.getChunkSampler()
